CareerBandhuv provides career information and guidance for general informational
purposes only. It is NOT a substitute for professional career counselling,
academic advising, or legal employment advice.

- Career recommendations are generated by algorithms and AI and may not reflect
  your individual circumstances, local job market conditions, or personal factors.
- Salary ranges are indicative estimates and may vary by employer, location,
  experience, and economic conditions.
- The copyright holder makes no guarantee that following any career path,
  skill recommendation, or guidance provided by this Software will result in
  employment, income, or career success.
- Users are responsible for independently verifying career information and
  consulting qualified professionals before making significant life decisions.

All trademarks, certifications, and examination names (UPSC, IBPS, ICAI, etc.)
belong to their respective owners. CareerBandhuv is not affiliated with or
endorsed by any examination board, government body, or professional institute.
